column2: SELECT s.specObjID, g.h_alpha_flux, g.oiii_#_flux, g.nii_#_flux, g.h_beta_flux, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.velDisp, e.bpt FROM SpecObjAll AS s JOIN galSpecLine AS g ON s.specObjID = g.specObjID JOIN emissionLinesPort AS e ON s.specObjID = e.specObjID WHERE g.h_alpha_flux > # AND g.h_beta_flux > # AND g.oiii_#_flux > # AND g.nii_#_flux > # AND s.snMedian > # AND s.class = &&& AND e.bpt <> &&& AND e.bpt <> &&&
